/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a sense of being in the midst of the action. The sky above is a clear blue, providing a vibrant backdrop to the urban landscape. Buildings of various sizes and designs line the street, interspersed with trees that add a touch of green to the scene. Power lines crisscross above, a common sight in many cities. The sun shines brightly, casting light and shadows that add depth to the image.
